COMMENT ON COLUMN SYSTEM_EVENTS.EVENT_SEQ IS 'A sequence number to uniquely identify an event of a particular event type.  Incremented within each event type starting at 1.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN SYSTEM_EVENTS.EVENT_DATE IS 'The date the system event begins.';
